			<div class="entry-utility">
									<span class="cat-links">
						<a href="http://www.eyalo.com/category/bitcoin-2/" title="View all posts in Bitcoin" rel="category tag">Bitcoin</a>, <a href="http://www.eyalo.com/category/internet-2/" title="View all posts in Internet" rel="category tag">Internet</a>, <a href="http://www.eyalo.com/category/money-and-economy/" title="View all posts in Money and Economy" rel="category tag">Money and Economy</a>, <a href="http://www.eyalo.com/category/technology/" title="View all posts in Technology" rel="category tag">Technology</a>					</span>
